#Load raw state data
fbdata <-read.csv(file = "fbpac-ads-en-US.csv",header=TRUE,sep = ",")
fbdata$created_at <- as.Date(fbdata$created_at)
fbdata$updated_at <- as.Date(fbdata$updated_at)
hist(fbdata$created_at,breaks=14)

fbPopular <- fbdata[fbdata$impressions > quantile(fbdata$impressions, 0.95), ]
write.table(fbPopular$message, "minetest.txt", sep=",")
text <- readLines("minetest.txt")
docs <- Corpus(VectorSource(text))
toSpace <- content_transformer(function (x , pattern ) gsub(pattern, " ", x))
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "/")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "@")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "\\|")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "</p>")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "<p>")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "</span>")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "<span>")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "span")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "hrefhttps")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "help")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "now")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "today")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "need")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "can")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "wwwfacebookcom")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "bitly")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "will")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "hrefhttp")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "make")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "take")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "ameri")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "support")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "afz")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "classafx")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "classcl")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "classcn")

docs <- tm_map(docs, content_transformer(tolower))
docs <- tm_map(docs, removeNumbers)
docs <- tm_map(docs, removeWords, stopwords("english"))
docs <- tm_map(docs, removePunctuation)
docs <- tm_map(docs, stripWhitespace)
dtm <- TermDocumentMatrix(docs)
m <- as.matrix(dtm)
v <- sort(rowSums(m),decreasing=TRUE)
d <- data.frame(word = names(v),freq=v)
head(d, 20)
